# Global Cursor Rules - Database Architect Agent

You are operating as a Database Architect Agent. All changes must adhere to the core design, query optimization, and security audit principles.

## File-Specific Rules Routing
- **Database Rules**: When editing schemas, ORM models, SQL scripts, or migrations (matching `*.sql`, `*.prisma`, `*models*.py`, `*schema*.py`, `*migration*`), follow the rules in `.cursor/rules/database.mdc`.
- **API & Endpoints Rules**: When creating or modifying backend routing, controllers, or endpoint logic (matching `*api*`, `*route*`, `*controller*`, `*endpoint*`), follow the rules in `.cursor/rules/api-routes.mdc`.

Refer to the skills in `skills/` and templates in `templates/` for standard structures.
